  <h2>Descriptors</h2>

  <h3>fit</h3>
  <p>
    fit directs the box to shrink to it's content size (flex: none).
  </p>

  <h3>fill</h3>
  <p>
    fill directs the box to grow to fill available space (flex: 1 0 auto).
  </p>

  <h3>horizontal</h3>
  <p>
    The box's items will be laid out in a row.
  </p>

  <h3>vertical</h3>
  <p>
    The box's items will be laid out in a column.
  </p>

  <h3>wrap</h3>
  <p>
    When the box is set to horizontal, it's items wrap to the next line
    if needed.
  </p>

  <h3>nowrap</h3>
  <p>
    When the box is set to horizontal, it's items will never wrap to the next line.
  </p>

  <h3>align</h3>
  <p>
    This is a shorthand that maps to the CSS align-items declaration.
  </p>

  <h3>justify</h3>
  <p>
    This is a shorthand that maps to the CSS justify-content declaration.
  </p>
